{
  "stem": "1419.4",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I would like to also to mention to you, I had-- I didn't tell you about Zakopane.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was in this-- the first camp, in the [GERMAN], working camp in Zakopane, the stone quarry.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were not allowed to go home.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Just once a month, we were allowed to go-- certain people were allowed to go home.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Not by train.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Either by foot or we-- sometimes we rented a driver which worked for the-- for the-- for the German company.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he took us on the-- on the big truck and took us home, and he picked us up the next day.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Everybody gave a few zlotys to go home to pick up some clothes and pick up some food which, which were available, because we were getting some food in the, the camp.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So one day, it was in 1941, one day, there was the order given that we were not allowed to go home.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were quite, quite upset about it and surprised.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Why we not go home?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We don't-- we don't have no, no, no-- we couldn't-- we washed our own clothes over there, but we had to change clothes somehow.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And sometimes we bring something, some little bit of food from the house, and we would like to see the families, too.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was no time to, to write letters or call somebody.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You, you didn't-- just didn't do it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I was elected-- I knew the, the, the meister then.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I spoke German.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I was elected to go to ask him if he would allow a few people to go home to bring there some clothes or something for, for the rest of us.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So I, I went.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He lived in a villa.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We were not exactly-- there were not barbed wire.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
